gnosis.md\",\"content\":\"Ticket: 000_diagnosis\\n\\nObjective:\\nReproduce failing tests and locate the bug in separability_matrix for nested CompoundModels.\\n\\nTasks:\\n- Run failing tests: astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model6-result6] and ::test_separable[compound_model9-result9]\\n- Add small reproducer script demonstrating the incorrect separability_matrix output for nested CompoundModels (as in issue description)\\n- Inspect astropy.modeling.separable.separability_matrix implementation and related code paths handling CompoundModel\\n- Determine whether nested CompoundModels are flattened before computing separability or whether connectivity computation incorrectly aggregates indices\\n- Produce diagnosis notes and propose a minimal fix (e.g., have separability_matrix flatten nested compound models or adjust index mapping)\\n\\nAssignee: Engineer\\nEstimate: 2-4h\\n\\nAcceptance criteria:\\n- Reproducer that shows failing behavior\\n- Path to the cause identified with suggested fix\\n\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}], "content": null}, {"content": "Successfully wrote to /home/cerberose/mas-evaluate-script/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board/astropy-12907/000_diagnosis.md", "role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_mbVXZkH1xXGbPEC4Wep4KxCh"}, {"role": "assistant", "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_szYDLt5jjko5ejgccpePDD6C", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\":\"data/project_board/astropy-12907/001_fix.md\",\"content\":\"Ticket: 001_fix\\n\\nObjective:\\nImplement minimal fix so separability_matrix correctly handles nested CompoundModels.\\n\\nTasks:\\n- Based on diagnosis, modify separability_matrix to either flatten nested CompoundModels (preferred) or correctly map input/output indices when encountering nested CompoundModels\\n- Ensure changes are minimal and localized to astropy/modeling/separable.py (or appropriate module)\\n- Run unit tests related to modeling/separable\\n\\nAssignee: Engineer\\nEstimate: 2-6h\\n\\nAcceptance criteria:\\n- Tests from failing list pass locally\\n- No unrelated tests broken\\n- Implementation includes comments explaining handling of CompoundModel\\n\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}], "content": null}, {"content": "Successfully wrote to /home/cerberose/mas-evaluate-script/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board/astropy-12907/001_fix.md", "role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_szYDLt5jjko5ejgccpePDD6C"}, {"role": "assistant", "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_uQ0c9H60X44XpxcqvoDgGqOt", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\":\"data/project_board/astropy-12907/002_tests.md\",\"content\":\"Ticket: 002_tests\\n\\nObjective:\\nAdd unit tests covering nested CompoundModel separability cases to prevent regressions.\\n\\nTasks:\\n- Add tests in astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py that cover nested CompoundModel cases (reproducer from issue)\\n- Ensure tests assert correct separability_matrix\\n- Run pytest for modeling tests\\n\\nAssignee: Engineer\\nEstimate: 1-2h\\n\\nAcceptance criteria:\\n- New tests added and passing\\n- CI coverage for nested CompoundModel separability ensured\\n\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}], "content": null}, {"content": "Successfully wrote to /home/cerberose/mas-evaluate-script/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board/astropy-12907/002_tests.md", "role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_uQ0c9H60X44XpxcqvoDgGqOt"}, {"role": "assistant", "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_bEtyw5J2PeWIRIbiShMHuGFD", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\":\"data/project_board/astropy-12907/003_review.md\",\"content\":\"Ticket: 003_review\\n\\nObjective:\\nCode review for the change to separability_matrix.\\n\\nTasks:\\n- Review the implementation for correctness, readability, and minimal surface area\\n- Ensure that flattening nested CompoundModels (if applied) does not change external behav